name: OptionalTypo Style LORA
description:
This is my first attempt at the Artist optionalTypo

It gives somewhat an oldschool anime feel like 1990's style but it needs a little help from "flat_color"

Hope to hear your thoughts
It was trained over AbyssOrangeMix 2 Hard

All the preview images use

DPM++ 2M Karras 30 Steps 320x320 Hires x2 CFG 11-13 Denoising at 0.55

Recomended weight: 0.65 and (flat_color:0.9)

Thanks to AOM it does some NSFW
